#                            **Task Manager App**

---

<div align="center">

A modern, feature-rich task management app with **multi-user profiles**, stunning themes, detailed analytics, and image export.  
Built completely with **vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. Fully client-side. Deploy instantly on **Vercel**.

🔗 [Live Demo](https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/)

</div>

---

## ✨ **Key Features**

|   |   |
| :------------------------------- | :------------------------------------------- |
| **🎨 Multiple Color Themes**      | **👤 User Profile System**                   |
| 6 beautiful themes: Blue, Forest, Sunset, Berry, Ocean, Rose.<br>Instant theme switching.<br>Theme persists for each user. | Multi-user accounts: register and switch.<br>Choose from 8 avatar emojis.<br>Edit profile details.<br>Each user has their own tasks. |
| **📋 Enhanced Task Management**   | **🔍 Advanced Filtering & Sorting**          |
| Detailed tasks: title, description, category, priority, due date, estimated time.<br>Track 0–100% progress.<br>Smart overdue indicators.<br>Inline editing and bulk actions.| Filter by status and category.<br>Sort by Newest, Oldest, Due Date, Priority, or Alphabetical.<br>Combine filters for instant searches. |
| **📊 Analytics & Visualization**  | **📸 Image Export**                          |
| Live progress bar & completion percentage.<br>Interactive doughnut chart (Chart.js).<br>Stats on pending, completed, priorities, overdue.| Download tasks as PNG.<br>Export your profile card as image.<br>Print-ready layouts. |
| **📱 Mobile & Accessibility**     |                                              |
| Responsive design for all devices.<br>Touch-optimized controls.<br>Accessible for screen readers.<br>Keyboard shortcuts (e.g. Ctrl+N for new task).<br>Offline ready. |                                              |

---

## 🚀 **Quick Start**

**Local Development**
1. Clone/download the repository  
2. Open `index.html` in a modern browser  
3. Register or log in  
4. Start managing tasks!

**Deploy to Vercel**
1. Push repository to GitHub  
2. Import on [Vercel](https://vercel.com/)  
3. Deploy instantly as a static site  

---

## 📁 **Project Structure**

task-manager-app/
├── index.html # Main app UI
├── css/
│ └── style.css # All themes & responsive styles
├── js/
│ ├── storage.js # Multi-user localStorage API
│ ├── ui.js # UI rendering, image export, analytics
│ └── app.js # Core logic & user management
├── libs/
│ └── html2canvas.min.js # For image exports
└── README.md # Documentation (this file)


---

## 🔒 **Privacy & Security**

- 100% client-side: no backend, no server
- Per-user data saved in **localStorage**
- No analytics, tracking, or data sharing
- You fully control exports and deletions

---

## 🎯 **Performance & Optimization**

| Feature   | Details                 |
|:----------|:-----------------------|
| Size      | <100KB total           |
| Rendering | Efficient DOM updates  |
| Device    | Battery/memory friendly|
| Loading   | Instant, works offline |

---

## 📞 **Support & Troubleshooting**

- **Reset app:** Clear browser localStorage  
- **JS required:** JavaScript must be enabled in browser  
- **Browsers:** Use up-to-date Chrome, Edge, Firefox, Safari  
- **Console:** For errors, open browser developer console  

**Known Limitations**
- Storage: limited by browser (~5–10MB per user)
- No cloud/data sync (local only)
- Image export clarity relies on browser

