## 🔭 **Future Scope & Ideas**

- **🔄 Cloud Sync:**  
  - Integrate secure cloud backup and multi-device sync (Google Drive, Dropbox, account-based sync)
- **📱 PWA Support:**  
  - Fully installable Progressive Web App with push notifications, add to home-screen
- **📤 Data Export/Import Formats:**  
  - JSON, CSV, PDF export; one-click restore/import  
- **🤝 Collaboration:**  
  - Shared task lists and real-time collaboration (teams, families)
- **📅 Calendar Integration:**  
  - Sync due dates with Google/Outlook calendar
- **⏰ Reminders:**  
  - Browser or push notifications for upcoming and overdue tasks
- **💬 Natural Language Input:**  
  - Add tasks with smart parsing: “Buy milk tomorrow at 5pm”
- **🗂️ Custom Categories & Tags:**  
  - User-defined categories, color tags, label management
- **🏷️ Task Templates:**  
  - Quick-add common routines (e.g. daily chores)
- **🔗 Integration:**  
  - Webhooks, productivity integrations (Trello, Todoist, Slack, Zapier)
- **📊 Reports & Insights:**  
  - Downloadable activity/performance reports over time, trends & streaks
- **🎮 Gamification:**  
  - Earn badges, streaks, level-ups for continued productivity!

